      <guid>/docs/machinelearning/models/classification/multi-class/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;br&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;label-smoothing&#34;&gt;Label Smoothing&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://paperswithcode.com/method/label-smoothing&#34;&gt;Label Smoothing&lt;/a&gt; is a regularization technique that introduces noise for the labels.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://arxiv.org/pdf/1906.02629.pdf&#34;&gt;When Does Label Smoothing Help?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We show that label smoothing encourages the representations of training examples from the same class to group in tight clusters.
This results in loss of information in the logits about resemblances between instances of different classes, which is necessary for distillation, but does not hurt generalization or calibration of the model’s predictions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://medium.com/@nainaakash012/when-does-label-smoothing-help-89654ec75326&#34;&gt;When Does Label Smoothing Help? Medium post&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://towardsdatascience.com/what-is-label-smoothing-108debd7ef06&#34;&gt;What is Label Smoothing?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.pyimagesearch.com/2019/12/30/label-smoothing-with-keras-tensorflow-and-deep-learning/&#34;&gt;Label smoothing with Keras, TensorFlow, and Deep Learning&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.kaggle.com/shahules/tackle-with-label-smoothing-proved&#34;&gt;Kaggle notebook&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://towardsdatascience.com/label-smoothing-making-model-robust-to-incorrect-labels-2fae037ffbd0&#34;&gt;Label Smoothing: An ingredient of higher model accuracy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://www.4betterhealthmedicine.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Screen-Shot-2019-06-09-at-1.20.23-AM.png&#34; alt=&#34;Smoothie&#34;&gt;&lt;br&gt;
